snippet.title: Feed Me (Nitrome.com) Levels 1-5
snippet.description:
First 5 levels of Feed Me, a game about a venus flytrap that has a very long neck and can move around the levels by biting the walls to reach them until finding the exit door.
You can play the game in: http://www.nitrome.com/games/feedme/?game=feedme#.X2Kitef45PY
I hope you like it!
